<div id="u-credit-00140-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leeeeeeoooooo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6158338); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6158338&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200729" alt="LEEEEEEOOOOOO" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6158338)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/leeeeeeoooooo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6158338); return false;">LEEEEEEOOOOOO</a></span></p>
