<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6306406&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200729" alt="ScorpionidaSlaughter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6306406)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;">ScorpionidaSlaughter</a></span></p>
