<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/on-no" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5637670); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5637670&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200730" alt="on-no" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5637670)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/on-no" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5637670); return false;">on-no</a></span></p>
