<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00067/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong><strong>《scp基金会使命宣言》</strong>中文版,悬挂于Site-CN-13中央大厅。任何完整阅读过此项目的基金会工作人员将会在24小时内大幅提高工作效率，并处于亢奋状态，对基金会持有极度的信任与忠诚。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>未被回收，也无需回收。<br />
<strong>发现时间：</strong>2020/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Site-CN-13</span>未被回收，也无需回收。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>仍悬挂于Site-CN-13中央大厅，被用中式裱框装裱。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>这真的百看不厌！为基金会效力，为人类安全工作真令我感到荣幸！——特工 林██</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00067" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00067" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00067-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fishbone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6127045); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6127045&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200730" alt="Dr Fishbone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6127045)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fishbone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6127045); return false;">Dr Fishbone</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1587020626 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">16 Apr 2020 07:03</span></p>
</div>
